  +files/flac-1.1.3.patch, stratagus-2.1.ebuild:
  Added patch from Josh Coalson (from FLAC) and closing bug #157586.

  04 Dec 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org> stratagus-2.1.ebuild:
  Removing old virtual/x11 dependency.

  19 Oct 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> stratagus-2.1.ebuild:
  Depend on 1.1.2 version of flac, as the 1.1.3 version changes API.

  13 Jan 2006; Stefan Schweizer <genstef@gentoo.org> stratagus-2.1.ebuild:
  Add modular depends

  24 Sep 2005; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org> stratagus-2.1.ebuild:
